<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 12:28:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>印度表示已向中国转达了对西藏水电站大坝的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</link><description>印度外交部周五表示，新德里已就中国计划在流入印度的雅鲁藏布江上修建西藏水电站的计划向北京表达了担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 11:12:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-says-conveyed-concerns-china-over-hydropower-dam-tibet-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：华尔街连续五天下跌，美元占主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-03/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 11:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>C919喷气式飞机制造商中国商飞的目标是到2026年开通东南亚航班</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-maker-c919-jet-aims-southeast-asian-flights-by-2026-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司的一位高级官员告诉中国媒体，其目标是到 2026 年其 C919 喷气式飞机开始执飞飞往东南亚的商业航线，这是其走出国内市场的第一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 10:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-maker-c919-jet-aims-southeast-asian-flights-by-2026-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲黄金 印度黄金需求滞后；农历新年前夕中国保费上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-gold-demand-lags-china-premiums-rise-ahead-lunar-new-year-2025-01-03/</link><description>印度的黄金折扣本周保持稳定，因为价格上涨使买家望而却步，而中国经销商因预期即将到来的农历新年之前需求强劲而收取更高的溢价。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 08:52:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-india-gold-demand-lags-china-premiums-rise-ahead-lunar-new-year-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国为政府工作人员提供十年来首次大幅加薪以提振经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</link><description>受此举影响的人士表示，中国各地数百万政府工作人员本周意外加薪，因为北京方面希望增加支出以支持经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 07:19:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-gives-government-workers-first-big-pay-bump-decade-boost-economy-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>随着外国手机销量连续第四个月下滑，苹果在中国的麻烦加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/foreign-smartphone-shipments-china-slump-47-november-2025-01-03/</link><description>一家政府下属研究公司周五公布的数据显示，11 月份包括苹果公司 iPhone 在内的外国品牌智能手机对中国的出货量同比下降 47.4%，连续第四个月下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 07:15:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/foreign-smartphone-shipments-china-slump-47-november-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国设立新的国家体育仲裁中心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</link><description>中国本周在首都北京开设了首个国家体育仲裁中心，为加强解决体育纠纷和保护运动员权利的法律框架迈出了关键一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 06:45:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-sets-up-new-national-sports-arbitration-centre-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>在商业航空经历了致命的一年之后，中国敦促进行安全评估</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</link><description>继2018年以来全球商业航空死亡人数最多的一年之后，中国当局呼吁对行业风险进行评估，以发现从航线到跑道的任何“隐藏”运营风险。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 05:49:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-urges-safety-assessments-after-deadly-year-commercial-aviation-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>受印度、韩国供应影响，新加坡 12 月航油进口量创多年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-dec-jet-fuel-imports-hit-multi-year-high-india-s-korea-supply-2025-01-03/</link><description>贸易消息人士和船舶追踪数据显示，新加坡的航空燃油进口量可能在去年 12 月创下多年来的新高，其中印度是最大的供应国，因为对欧洲的套利活动仍然关闭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/singapores-dec-jet-fuel-imports-hit-multi-year-high-india-s-korea-supply-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>2025年中国将大幅增加国债融资刺激经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</link><description>一位国家规划官员周五表示，中国将在 2025 年大幅增加超长期国债资金，以刺激商业投资和消费刺激计划，同时北京将加大财政刺激力度，以重振步履蹒跚的经济。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 04:22:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-will-sharply-increase-funding-treasury-bonds-spur-growth-2025-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉2024年中国销量创历史新高，逆势全球下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-rise-record-high-83000-december-2025-01-03/</link><description>美国电动汽车制造商特斯拉周五表示，2024 年其中国销量增长 8.8%，达到超过 657,000 辆汽车的历史新高，在竞争激烈的市场中表现强劲，全球年度交付量首次下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-sales-rise-record-high-83000-december-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>海南免税消费大幅下滑，中国购物天堂陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</link><description>去年，由于经济疲软导致国内游客数量急剧下降，LVMH 和开云集团等全球奢侈品牌都在中国海南省开设了门店，免税支出下降了 29.3%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/trouble-chinas-shopping-paradise-hainan-duty-free-spending-falls-29-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>美元接近两年高点，股市陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-03/</link><description>周五，美元兑其他货币汇率维持在两年高点附近，因投资者押注美国和其他地区的经济增长差距将扩大，而中国蓝筹股遭遇 2022 年以来最大单周跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 02:36:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>市场关注中国政策支持，油价将每周上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-two-month-highs-optimism-over-policy-support-growth-2025-01-03/</link><description>油价周五小幅下跌，但在前一交易日收于两个多月来最高点后，受中国潜在进一步经济刺激和美国利率下降的支撑，本周仍有望上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 01:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-rises-two-month-highs-optimism-over-policy-support-growth-2025-01-03/</guid></item><item><title>Skydance 和派拉蒙驳回对 84 亿美元合并计划的反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/skydance-paramount-dismiss-objections-planned-84-bln-merger-2025-01-03/</link><description>Skydance Media 和派拉蒙全球公司周四为其 84 亿美元的合并计划进行了辩护，敦促联邦通信委员会驳回批评者的反对意见，称其“毫无根据”且“毫无价值”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:45:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/skydance-paramount-dismiss-objections-planned-84-bln-merger-2025-01-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>